2002-12-12  Raphaël Poss  <raph@lrde.epita.fr>

	* oln.m4 (AC_NUMERIC_LIMITS, AC_CXX_C99_MATH): Add new macros...
	* oln/config/system.hh: ... and use them instead of ugly detection
	systems.

	* oln/config/system.hh: Fix bug.
	* oln/config/pconf.hh: Fix bug.

2002-12-11  Raphaël Poss  <raph@lrde.epita.fr>

	* Makefile.am (m4datadir, dist_m4data_DATA): Add for
	oln.m4. (EXAMPLE_IMGS, dist_pkgdata_DATA): Add for images.

	* oln/Makefile.am (pkginclude_HEADERS): Use instead of
	nobase_inst_HEADERS.

	* configure.ac: The testsuite is now optional. Depend again on
	Automake 1.7.1.

	* ChangeLog: Create. Old version moves to ../attic.
	* tests/ChangeLog: Remove. Old version moves to ../attic.
